如果想要从一个`List`对象中去掉某个字段重复的值所对应的对象，可以按照以下步骤进行操作：

1. 定义一个函数来判断两个对象的某个字段是否相同：

```java
public static boolean isEqual(Object obj1, Object obj2, String fieldName) throws NoSuchFieldException, IllegalAccessException {
    Field field = obj1.getClass().getDeclaredField(fieldName);
    field.setAccessible(true);
    Object value1 = field.get(obj1);
    Object value2 = field.get(obj2);
    return value1.equals(value2);
}
```

该函数需要传入两个对象和一个字段名，它会获取两个对象指定字段的值并比较它们是否相同。

2. 通过遍历`List`对象，去掉重复的对象：

```java
public static void removeDuplicate(List<?> list, String fieldName) throws NoSuchFieldException, IllegalAccessException {
    for (int i = 0; i < list.size(); i++) {
        Object obj1 = list.get(i);

        for (int j = i + 1; j < list.size(); j++) {
            Object obj2 = list.get(j);

            if (isEqual(obj1, obj2, fieldName)) {
                list.remove(j);
                j--;
            }
        }
    }
}
```

该函数需要传入一个`List`对象和一个字段名，它会遍历整个`List`对象，并对每个对象与其余对象进行比较，如果发现有字段值相同的对象，则将后面的对象从`List`中删除。

下面是一个完整的示例代码：

```java
import java.lang.reflect.Field;
import java.util.ArrayList;
import java.util.List;

public class RemoveDuplicateTest {

    public static void main(String[] args) throws NoSuchFieldException, IllegalAccessException {
        List<Person> personList = new ArrayList<>();
        personList.add(new Person("张三", 20));
        personList.add(new Person("李四", 22));
        personList.add(new Person("王五", 20));
        personList.add(new Person("张三", 23));
        System.out.println("去重前：" + personList);

        removeDuplicate(personList, "name");

        System.out.println("去重后：" + personList);
    }

    public static boolean isEqual(Object obj1, Object obj2, String fieldName) throws NoSuchFieldException, IllegalAccessException {
        Field field = obj1.getClass().getDeclaredField(fieldName);
        field.setAccessible(true);
        Object value1 = field.get(obj1);
        Object value2 = field.get(obj2);
        return value1.equals(value2);
    }

    public static void removeDuplicate(List<?> list, String fieldName) throws NoSuchFieldException, IllegalAccessException {
        for (int i = 0; i < list.size(); i++) {
            Object obj1 = list.get(i);

            for (int j = i + 1; j < list.size(); j++) {
                Object obj2 = list.get(j);

                if (isEqual(obj1, obj2, fieldName)) {
                    list.remove(j);
                    j--;
                }
            }
        }
    }

    private static class Person {
        public String name;
        public int age;

        public Person(String name, int age) {
            this.name = name;
            this.age = age;
        }

        @Override
        public String toString() {
            return "Person{" +
                    "name='" + name + '\'' +
                    ", age=" + age +
                    '}';
        }
    }
}
```

上述示例代码中，`Person`类有两个字段`name`和`age`。我们以`name`字段为例，定义了一个`removeDuplicate()`函数去重`List<Person>`对象中的重复元素。执行该函数后，控制台输出结果为：

```
去重前：[Person{name='张三', age=20}, Person{name='李四', age=22}, Person{name='王五', age=20}, Person{name='张三', age=23}]
去重后：[Person{name='张三', age=20}, Person{name='李四', age=22}, Person{name='王五', age=20}]
```

